going to be--

00:09:02.270 --> 00:09:04.770
this treaty does need
to be updated.

00:09:04.770 --> 00:09:05.780
It is really out of date.

00:09:05.780 --> 00:09:08.910
It was last touched in 1988.

00:09:08.910 --> 00:09:10.950
And ultimately the biggest thing
that's going on here

00:09:10.950 --> 00:09:14.230
is-- or rather in Dubai, I
should say-- is whether this

00:09:14.230 --> 00:09:17.950
binding international treaty
and the ITU's corresponding

00:09:17.950 --> 00:09:21.800
mandate should be expanded to
internet and internet policy.

00:09:21.800 --> 00:09:26.130
This would represent a really
big shift away from the open,

00:09:26.130 --> 00:09:29.760
multi-stakeholder institutions
that currently doing internet

00:09:29.760 --> 00:09:31.200
policy making.

00:09:31.200 --> 00:09:33.650
Another sort of random alphabet
soup-- we have ICANN,

00:09:33.650 --> 00:09:36.320
the International Corporation
for Assigned Names Numbers;

00:09:36.320 --> 00:09:39.170
the IETF, the Internet
Engineering Task Force; the

00:09:39.170 --> 00:09:40.770
EEE, and a variety of others.

00:09:40.770 --> 00:09:45.660
And the thing that really
differentiates from the ITU is

00:09:45.660 --> 00:09:48.900
that the ITU, only governments
have a vote.

00:09:48.900 --> 00:09:51.380
In order to join the ITU--

00:09:51.380 --> 00:09:55.430
the Secretary General likes to
make a big point that there

00:09:55.430 --> 00:09:56.770
are 700 sector members.

00:09:56.770 --> 00:09:58.800
But those 700 sector members
have to pay anywhere between

00:09:58.800 --> 00:10:01.350
$2,000 and $35,000
to be there.

00:10:01.350 --> 00:10:04.210
And they still can't
speak on the floor.

00:10:04.210 --> 00:10:05.820
And this stands in
sharp contrast to

00:10:05.820 --> 00:10:07.890
what we're doing here.

00:10:07.890 --> 00:10:10.830
In terms of the second point to
know about this process and

00:10:10.830 --> 00:10:12.800
what it's been like, the
preparatory process has been

00:10:12.800 --> 00:10:15.075
deeply flawed.

00:10:15.075 --> 00:10:18.110
