00:10:24.470 --> 00:10:26.530
And it really lacks
inclusivity.

00:10:26.530 --> 00:10:29.100
Users have not had a voice.

00:10:29.100 --> 00:10:31.850
So society by and large
hasn't had a voice.

00:10:31.850 --> 00:10:34.930
And so I think the third thing
to consider is that the ITU

00:10:34.930 --> 00:10:36.390
does good work.

00:10:36.390 --> 00:10:39.660
It does a lot of really
good work.

00:10:39.660 --> 00:10:42.530
We have to remember that this
is not just about the

00:10:42.530 --> 00:10:43.190
secretariat.

00:10:43.190 --> 00:10:46.560
This is really about member
states using the WCIT to play

00:10:46.560 --> 00:10:49.330
up their larger geopolitical
agendas.

00:10:49.330 --> 00:10:53.890
And so the authoritarian states
that are trying to

00:10:53.890 --> 00:10:56.970
