work that ITU does.

00:11:06.340 --> 00:11:11.110
And so there's less of
a need to expand--

00:11:11.110 --> 00:11:13.150
or less concerned with
expanding the ITU's

00:11:13.150 --> 00:11:15.070
mandate in this way.

00:11:15.070 --> 00:11:18.660
And then I think there's also
sort of a community of folks

00:11:18.660 --> 00:11:25.370
who are pushing back against
out-sized US influence in

00:11:25.370 --> 00:11:26.260
