00:16:04.220 --> 00:16:06.185
things that they are discussing,
the documents they

00:16:06.185 --> 00:16:08.440
are sharing, and that
kind of stuff.

00:16:08.440 --> 00:16:11.990
I will say that although this
discussion has been framed in

00:16:11.990 --> 00:16:17.660
some way as a take hands off
the internet from one side,

00:16:17.660 --> 00:16:22.860
and from the other side, this
idea of these governments,

00:16:22.860 --> 00:16:26.220
this government-centered
agenda trying to

00:16:26.220 --> 00:16:27.460
take over the internet.

00:16:27.460 --> 00:16:35.860
