00:21:27.070 --> 00:21:32.990
preparing ICT civil society
participants around the

00:21:32.990 --> 00:21:39.840
continent through a discussion
list and a wiki page in order

00:21:39.840 --> 00:21:45.260
for them to become more aware
of the issues at stake, and

00:21:45.260 --> 00:21:50.150
try to position their respective
governments in

00:21:50.150 --> 00:21:53.080
order to be informed about their
governments' positions

00:21:53.080 --> 00:21:58.240
and the preparatory process that
their governments engage

00:21:58.240 --> 00:22:02.190
in so that if possible, they
can even be part of the

00:22:02.190 --> 00:22:03.440
national delegation.

00:22:05.790 --> 00:22:10.180
