we go from integrating,

00:38:02.610 --> 00:38:07.520
collecting, and integrating
people's inputs and views into

00:38:07.520 --> 00:38:09.580
something that is actionable.

00:38:09.580 --> 00:38:11.540
That's what the IGF--

00:38:11.540 --> 00:38:12.730
Internet Governance Forum--

00:38:12.730 --> 00:38:14.540
has not been begged
to do so far.

00:38:14.540 --> 00:38:19.600
So if we can go back to a
formula like IGF but evolved,

00:38:19.600 --> 00:38:25.510
from the simple talk shop
to implementation, to

00:38:25.510 --> 00:38:29.550
recommendation, that would
be a good way to grow.

